channel.title: Cache Questions
channel.description:
Hey guys, so I tried updating my cache from 718 to 729..
So when I try to load my server, it stops at: "Fetching Updates 97%", as shown below: [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/2mh8ljl.jpg[/img]
I'm not 100% sure what the problem is, because as shown, it says the cache is Initing fine. [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/14jukr9.jpg[/img]
I've been told I need to pack the cache which I'm not sure how to do, and I assume it has something to do with adding the opcodes.
Any help would be appreciated..
